{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Create national standards for advanced information from exam boards in 2022",
        "additional_details": "At the moment, the quality and quantity of advanced information given to students is highly variable depending on both exam board and subject. Combined with variable amount of content removed from examinations, we believe this means exams may be unfair on students, and make the qualifications granted by them highly questionable. Creating national standards should help even out these issues, make the exams fairer and help legitimise their qualifications.",
        "background": "Create standards across England for the advanced information given out by exam boards for AS and A-Level, GCSE examinations in the summer of 2022.",
